snippet.title: "MEGA MAN X DiVE Offline" Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Mega Man X DiVE Offline is coming to Steam, iOS, and Android!
Dive into exciting side-scrolling action and power up iconic characters from multiple Mega Man series!
Mega Man X DiVE Offline launches in 2023!

Official Site:
 https://www.capcom-games.com/megaman/xdive-offline/en-us/

Discord: https://discord.gg/Capcom
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/CapcomUSA
Twitter: https://twitter.com/CapcomUSA_
